description: Retrieves a list of commits and changes to a specified file.

parameters.name: repositoryName
parameters.description: The name of the repository that contains the file.

parameters.name: filePath
parameters.description: The full path of the file whose history you want to retrieve, including the name of the file.

nested_items.name: revisionDag
nested_items.description: An array of FileVersion objects that form a directed acyclic graph (DAG) of the changes to the file made by the commits that changed the file.

nested_items.name: commitId
nested_items.description: The full SHA ID of the specified commit.

nested_items.name: treeId
nested_items.description: Tree information for the specified commit.

nested_items.name: parents
nested_items.description: A list of parent commits for the specified commit. Each parent commit ID is the full commit ID.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The commit message associated with the specified commit.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the user who made the specified commit.

nested_items.name: email
nested_items.description: The email address associated with the user who made the commit, if any.

nested_items.name: date
nested_items.description: The date when the specified commit was commited, in timestamp format with GMT offset.

nested_items.name: committer
nested_items.description: Information about the person who committed the specified commit, also known as the committer. Information includes the date in timestamp format with GMT offset, the name of the committer, and the email address for the committer, as configured in Git.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the user who made the specified commit.

nested_items.name: email
nested_items.description: The email address associated with the user who made the commit, if any.

nested_items.name: date
nested_items.description: The date when the specified commit was commited, in timestamp format with GMT offset.

nested_items.name: additionalData
nested_items.description: Any other data associated with the specified commit.

nested_items.name: blobId
nested_items.description: The blob ID of the object that represents the content of the file in this version.

nested_items.name: path
nested_items.description: The name and path of the file at which this blob is indexed which contains the data for this version of the file. This value will vary between file versions if a file is renamed or if its path changes.

nested_items.name: revisionChildren
nested_items.description: An array of commit IDs that contain more recent versions of this file. If there are no additional versions of the file, this array will be empty.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: An enumeration token that can be used to return the next batch of results.
